    NameMapper
    Interface for mapping entity and typelist values between Guidwire applications for use in the ABContactAPI. The ABContactAPI XmlBackedInstance is expressed in terms of the datamodel for ContactManager. Other applications need to translate their entity and typelist values from the application datamodel to the ContactManager datamodel (XSD). This class will have concrete subclasses for each application which specify the files used to map the names between the datamodels.
    NameMapperBase
    Base class for mapping entity and typelist values between Guidwire applications for use in the ABContactAPI. The ABContactAPI XmlBackedInstance is expressed in terms of the datamodel for ContactManager. Other applications need to translate their entity and typelist values from the application datamodel to the ContactManager datamodel (XSD). This class will have concrete subclasses for each application which specify the files used to map the names between the datamodels.
    NameMapperImpl<T extends NameMapperImpl<T>>
    Abstract base class for NameMapper implementations. This class will have concrete subclasses for each application which specify the files used to map the names between the datamodels.
